[{"id":2378,"date":"2023-10-22T17:00:00","modified":"2023-10-21T19:50:19","slug":"star-atlas-weekly-news-recap-83","link":"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/newsletter\/star-atlas-weekly-news-recap-83\/","title":{"rendered":"Star Atlas Weekly News Recap #83"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald.  Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We are looking for guests to be on our podcast.  The podcast is a discussion of the past week&#8217;s news about Star Atlas.  If you are interested in being on the podcast, please <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/contact\/\">contact us<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We are launching a Star Atlas merch store.  Please check it out at <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticgear.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Intergalactic Gear<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We are creating a &#8220;non-guild&#8221; guild.  If you are interested in learning more, please go to <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticcoalition.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Intergalactic Coalition<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">If you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Star Atlas Sage Labs HOT TIPS!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Beyond the Horizon posted a video with some <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=3j8_LYtvMIs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">tips on playing SAGE Labs<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Metaverse Nomads #116 Star Atlas w\/ @Santiacc_<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Metaverse Nomads posted a replay of their <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=wWzelQsKfWQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">weekly Star Atlas livestream<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>WEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #101<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Aephia posted their <a href=\"https:\/\/aephia.com\/star-atlas\/weekly-star-atlas-newsletter-101\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">weekly Star Atlas Newsletter<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>14 | My ULTIMATE Plan for Star Atlas!!!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Pathfinder posted a video about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=I9iJnhlmdMc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">his thoughts on Star Atlas<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Star Atlas Recap Oct 17 2023<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Beyond the Horizon posted a video recapping <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=S4M29nz3HcU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">recent Star Atlas news<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>STAR ATLAS #202 Updates on THE GAME!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">MetaVerse Explorer posted a video of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=y75_WabDv1M\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas updates<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Navigating Star Atlas #1 &#8211; The Vision with CPO Danny Floyd<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Star Atlas posted a video interview with the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=aHmp7HNk6gM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Star Atlas CPO Danny Floyd<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>The Atlas Brew #84<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Star Atlas TV posted a video replay of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=reJ1HGoDeOg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">latest Atlas Brew<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Star Atlas Brew #84: Michael Wagner &#8211; TLDR<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">TLDR posted a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=UJ6AwLo9cng\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">recap of the latest Atlas Brew<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>How to Stay Updated on Star Atlas<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Atlas Theory posted a video about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=gFexuai6ee4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">how to stay updated on Star Atlas<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>STAR ATLAS #203 New Patch With New Ship that SCANS FOR FREE!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">MetaVerse Explorer posted <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=HGRVy66_d9k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">another video of Star Atlas updates<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week. We are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week&#8217;s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4}]